## Your Task

Design {{ chapter_brief.get("scene_count", 3) }} scenes for this chapter. For each scene, specify all fields in the SceneBrief schema:

- ordinal, pov_character, location, time_marker
IMPORTANT: Be concise. Each field should be a phrase or single sentence.

- purpose (1 sentence), conflict (1 sentence), stakes (1 sentence), revelation (1 sentence or null)
- emotional_turn (1 sentence, e.g. "reluctance to resolve")
- dramatic_function (one word: establishment, escalation, pivot, relief, climax)
- characters_present (list of names)
- prohibited_moves (short phrases, 1-3 items)
- themes_touched, symbols_touched (lists of names)
- setup_links, payoff_links (short phrases, 1-3 items each)
- state_mutations: {key: "what changed"} — brief entries only
- is_pivotal: true/false

Respond with a JSON object matching the ScenePlanResponse schema.
